Quickstrike:




It took Quickstrike and Wildfire at least three days of constant 
movement to get back to Africa. They moved their way as one back to 
the area where the council base was. They stayed at least a mile away 
to make sure they were not seen or picked up by a scanner. 
Quickstrike stayed by Wildfire' side to stay in her range of pshyic 
abilities, and be able to read the mind ambient.
